<body lang=3D"en-IL" link=3D"#0563C1" vlink=3D"#954F72" style=3D"word-wrap:=
break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Dear investors,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I hope this mail finds you well.</span><o:p></o=
:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please find attached an Executive Summary of Q2=
 2022 activity.</span><span lang=3D"HE" dir=3D"RTL"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Also, you received an additional mail from the =
fund's administrator (Tzur) with a link to the following documents:<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;ms=
o-list:l0 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Financial Statements for Q2-2022<o:p></o:p></span></li=
><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;m=
so-list:l0 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Capital Account as of June 30, 2022<o:p></o:p></span><=
/li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:lef=
t;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Capital Call Notice <o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">In addition, On February 27, 2022, the Israeli =
Tax Authority issued an addendum to the tax ruling granted to Stardom Media=
 Ventures, LP (the &quot;Partnership&quot;) on February
 16, 2020, which requires making technical amendments in the Third Amended =
and Restated Limited Partnership Agreement of the Partnership. Accordingly,=
 the general partner of the Partnership had made the required amendments pu=
rsuant to the authority granted
 to it under Section 13.1.1 of the LPA. Please see attached for your record=
s the amended form of the LPA, in a marked changes version and in a clean e=
xecuted version.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please let me know if you have any further ques=
tions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Best regards,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Aviran</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" dir=3D"RTL"><span dir=3D"LTR"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></spa=
